Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Parti mis tuelo morow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu spinzzio tilatto cul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come to hear of this road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At a recent stop in a Poroson tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear the rumors about the wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.96,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm in a hurry, so I decided to take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask anything at all. Is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that you could hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:52.77,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\fscx105\fs80\fnMailart Rubberstamp\c&H7A8995&\pos(640,458)}Wolf and the Shepherd's Lamb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stave off wolves as well as care for sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hire me, I can protect you from wolves during your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you consider it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Enek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a moment while I ask my companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Her skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's skilled, she might be worth hiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard us, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have me, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know having you by my side is more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's never occurred to me to use a shepherd to drive off wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be a new business in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Human males like to have as many females as possible, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not being blinded by her charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're much cuter than her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's a passing mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what of her skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she'd be in the high range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a little more concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I could take a sheep from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but ordinary wolves wouldn't stand a chance, even in packs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very skilled at handling her dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The nastiest shepherds are the ones who have a clever dog that they share a strong bond with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks to me like both those things are true of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice suggests she's young, which means she'll get even nastier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should do something about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to hire her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hire her, she will be accompanying us for a time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I do not want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lubinheigen's only two days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Still no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor did I say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but bear with it for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I only want to see how effective a shepherd is against wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me. {\i1}You're{\i0} the one who might have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if my identity is exposed while she's traveling with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted me to say something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to travel together, just the two of us."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I doubt I'll be exposed in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How does forty Trie for the trip to Lubinheigen sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With a bonus if we happen to be attacked by wolves but make it unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect. Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I inquire as to your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Norah Arendt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Enek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been a shepherd long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just four years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I began my time as a shepherd when I first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped at an almshouse attached to an abbey and in return was allowed to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was relying on the almshouse, I'd always wanted to find a real trade of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was good fortune meeting Enek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your prayers were surely answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can't help but think that I have God to thank for our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found him, he was in a sad state, covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,From wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, probably from bandits or mercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was cowering under an overhang on a hill with this staff in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:08:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say, I never would have expected you to offer to escort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly a common thing for shepherds to do, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I actually want to become a seamstress,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I need money to pay for the guild membership fees and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you could make more money from guarding merchants than from herding sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's hard to find unclaimed fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many shepherds in every safe area.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So all that's left are wolf-strewn fields, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolves sure can be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're clever and sly, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I speak ill of them, they may hear, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you stop this early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no problem. I know that shepherds have to get to sleep before the sun goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to watch over the sheep throughout the night, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When I look at their wool, I always wonder what kind of clothing it'll be made into.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You do a remarkable job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be in charge of more sheep, judging from your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's only by God's blessings that I'm entrusted with even this many.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge flock... I just couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your employer has no eye for skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time for a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I couldn't possibly do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies. We merchants tend to think about things based on loss and profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people change their employers often?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal, if one is unsatisfied with one's terms of employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me for asking, but might your employer be the Church?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my merchant's intuition speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm tending to the sheep of a Church pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been very considerate to me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wages may be low, but the Church will never cease to exist until God himself forsakes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be out of work, and you'll always have something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,God never said anything against doing work on the side, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:14.68,Default,,1,1,0,,When we arrive in Lubinheigen, I'll make sure to ask my fellow merchants whether they need a reliable escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'd really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard work, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daily care of one's tail is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you meant the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Norah Arendt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I did ask for your approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even relax and groom my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why couldn't you have done it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd done it in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did it here... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly seemed to enjoy your chat with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With Norah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else would I be talking about? The dog and sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to talk. I didn't have any reason to refuse, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I had a real conversation with a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even tell that she was uncomfortable speaking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was love at first sight, I wouldn't have the pleasure of seeing her fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Aren't I quite the smooth talker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't fit you! It doesn't fit you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to laugh so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's quite an ace you had up your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if your bad mood is gone, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it all seems so trivial now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it was a gift from the child herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:58.18,Default,,1,1,0,,It would have taken ten times as long to obtain transit documents if we had to sit through routine inspections.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a benefit of being employed by the Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's forty Trie, as promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I exchange these silver coins, won't it come out to forty-five?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it an investment by a greedy merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Investment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:21.04,Default,,1,1,0,,Now that I know such a skilled shepherd, I might come across an opportunity to turn a profit on wool sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be staying at the trading house of the Lohen Trading Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you stop by before you head out to the fields with your sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to introduce you to a few merchants in need of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have to stay on the path we traveled on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm allowed to move to Kasrata, Poroson, and even Lamtra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lamtra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't travel on the roundabout official route, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I take the shortcut through the forest, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That eerie forest makes even the bravest of knights blanch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no worries as long as I'm with Enek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I daresay you'll have plenty of business, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance for livestock is that way, so I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left to do now is go through customs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and head to Lemerio Trading to sell the armor that we obtained thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We're {\i1}also{\i0} going to buy peaches preserved in honey with what we earn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't buy any if they aren't selling any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances are they won't have it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make a fuss if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It prevents enemies from entering during times of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They use those holes to pour scalding oil on the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more of a castle than a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Letter of transit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,From Poroson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty sets of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Armor from Poroson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I purchased them wholesale from Latparon Trading. Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you pay the taxes? Cash or goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, with goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over two sets right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that rare to make a wholesale purchase from Poroson?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You may pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:17:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bureaucrats will always be unpleasant people regardless of where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That civil servant scoffed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing our pile of armor, he probably thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't act so high and mighty just because you're making money."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what he thought. We were able to enter town without a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's park our wagon and head to the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you now understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That hit the spot! Sir, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One beer coming up. You sure can hold your liquor, young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barely started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fallen for one who loves to spend money, but she's a real beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd be perfect if she didn't have a tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The liquor is good and the people lively. 'Tis a good city, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The liveliness comes at a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch yourselves around knights or mercenaries, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A quarrel with them means a world of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The trading house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up. You have froth on the side of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must you drag me along to this trading house with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I am a bit too lovely to be left unattended!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you get drunk and let your ears or tail show?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just grab you in my jaws, and we'd dash from the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can surely leap over those walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there an old tale about a knight and a girl like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where the knight carries the captive girl to safety?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the story, there's not a trace of romance in the idea of being carried away in a wolf's jaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't the sort that would look good getting rescued anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what is a trading house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Risk and accidents go hand in hand with business,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no one who will protect you from either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as knights wear armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we merchants protect ourselves by banding together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where we're going is a branch office of merchants who share the same birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This always brings me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the buildings in my hometown look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to have your home scattered across the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here while I take care of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you not going to bring me in and brag about how lucky you are to your countrymen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be done before you know it. If you wait nicely, I'll buy you some sweetbread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want any?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, you sad excuse of a merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wandering around here at this hour... Cares not a whit for making money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be better off as a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Great merchants earn their money without having to soil their shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The only stain is the ink upon their fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Running around the market all day is the sign of a third-rate merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've found yourself a way with words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop the "my son" nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? All in the Lohen Trading Union are my sons and daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I even know of all the times you wet your bedroll after we made camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:38.85,Default,,1,1,0,,Or should I mention the time you and your friends stole money and snuck off to the brothel, scared shitless?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a man called Lawrence come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence? I haven't even seen a mouse these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:44.97,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode: "Wolf and Conspiracies."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:49.99,Default,,0,0,15,,{\i1}Next Episode: "Wolf and Conspiracies."
